TCRA MIS
Instructions
1. Copy files to web root


Epicor Setup
1.Install SQL Server 2000 (port 1433)
	create dbs TCRAControl and TCRAData
	create alias localhost in SQL server Client Network utility (name: localhost, network libriaries: TCP/IP)
2.Install Epicor Server
3.Install Epicor Cliet
4.Database update Wizard (use sql server authentication,setup demo system)
	open - Accounts Receivable > processing > Invoices > Invoice Entry
	select register -> enter site id = 640 -> you will get 5 user temp licence for 90 days(save)
5.Restore DBs(TCRAControl and TCRAData)
	Select options and force overwrite
6.Setup rates
	open - MultiCurrency > processing > Exchanges Rates
7.Setup period
	open - Accounts Receivable > processing > change period
8. Install dot net framework from Epicor735sp1
9. Install crystal reports runtime from Epicor735sp1
	


